2018 Resource Pulse Microcolony Analysis

Analysis and model construction/selection

11/28/2018

# Import packages ---------------------------------------------------------
library(psych)
library(nlme)
library(car)
library(multcompView)
library(lsmeans)
library(tidyverse)
library(rcompanion)
# Repeated measures analysis ----------------------------------------------
corr.model = lme(true_mc_mass ~ treatment + date + treatment*date, 
                 random = ~ 1 | id,
                 data = mc1.df,
                 na.action = na.exclude)
ACF(corr.model) # Lag 1: 0.314
model.1 = lme(true_mc_mass ~ treatment + date + treatment*date, 
              random = ~ 1 | id,
              data = mc1.df,
              correlation = corAR1(form = ~ date | id,
                                   value = 0.314),
              na.action = na.exclude,
              method = "REML")
Anova(model.1)
Analysis of Deviance Table (Type II tests)

Response: true_mc_mass
               Chisq Df Pr(>Chisq)    
treatment      21.81  3  7.144e-05 ***
date           74.43  1  < 2.2e-16 ***
treatment:date 26.73  3  6.706e-06 ***
---
Signif. codes:  0 ‘***’ 0.001 ‘**’ 0.01 ‘*’ 0.05 ‘.’ 0.1 ‘ ’ 1
model.1.fixed = gls(true_mc_mass ~ treatment + date + treatment*date,
                    data = mc1.df,
                    method="REML",
                    na.action = na.exclude)
anova(model.1, model.1.fixed)
plot(model.1)

model.null = lme(true_mc_mass ~ 1,
                 random = ~ 1 | id,
                 data = mc1.df,
                 na.action = na.exclude)
nagelkerke(model.1, 
           model.null)
